title: "Certified Reductions of the Weight-6 Euler Sum at Dyadic Arguments: Corrected Revision"
message: "If you use this repository, please cite the corrected revision and this reproducibility repository."
type: software
authors:
  - family-names: Williams
    given-names: Keenan
repository-code: "https://github.com/keewillidevnet/S42-omega2-reproducibility"
