abstract: >
  Corrected reproducibility repository for S_{4,2}(x) at dyadic arguments.
  Implements the corrected x=1/2 exact closed form in a 13-element dyadic basis,
  the certified x=1/4 depth-2 relation, and records x=-1/2 as open.
